Source: rbus
Version: 2.7.0
Upstream-URL: https://github.com/rdkcentral/rbus.git
Upstream-Ref: v2.7.0
Build-Depends: libcurl4-openssl-dev, libmsgpack-dev, libcjson-dev, linenoise

Package: rbus
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Depends: linenoise, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: RDK Bus messaging system - runtime
 RDK Bus (RBus) is a lightweight, fast and efficient bus messaging system.
 It allows interprocess communication (IPC) and remote procedure call (RPC)
 between multiple process running on a hardware device. It supports the
 creation and use of a data model, which is a hierarchical tree of named
 objects with properties, events, and methods.
 .
 This package contains the runtime libraries and binaries.

Package: librbus-dev
Section: libdevel
Priority: optional
Depends: rbus (= ${version})
Description: RDK Bus messaging system - development files
 RDK Bus (RBus) is a lightweight, fast and efficient bus messaging system.
 It allows interprocess communication (IPC) and remote procedure call (RPC)
 between multiple process running on a hardware device.
 .
 This package contains the development headers and static libraries.
